Title: 2-Pack Regular Fit Cotton Dress Socks
Body (HTML): Two classic, solid pair of regular-length socks by BOSS, crafted in a mercerized stretch-cotton blend. Showcasing impeccable BOSS workmanship, these comfortable socks are made with highly resistant yarn and feature pressure-free, hand-linked toes, reinforced stress zones, and a soft-grip top band for reliable hold. Detailed with subtle logos for an iconic touch, this two-pack provides a refined foundation for business ensembles.
